Our services
Övik Energi AB expands their business and starts to build and provide an optical fiber network for internet connection.
The first electricity is generated in Örnsköldsvik by the company de Laval.
The municipal assembly of Örnsköldsvik decides to reconstruct Örnsköldsviks Energiverk into an incorporated company, owned by the municipality. The name is changed to Övik Energi AB.
We have a long history that spans over 120 years. Here is a short timeline of happenings that defines what we provide to you today.
